# Build context for the Plus API image is the repo root (see plus-api/Dockerfile),
# so keep the huge, irrelevant parts of the static site out of the Docker context.
# Only plus-api/ sources and plus/content-index.json are actually COPYed.
.git
**/node_modules
plus-api/dist
plus-api/.env
plus-api/scripts-dev

# Static-site content the API never needs (keeps the context small & builds fast).
*.html
assets
images
img
reports
notecast
insight
litecast
metanotes
chairside
glossary
card
tools
.dentcast
.github
